                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    <font face="Times New Roman" size="3">The Identifier External datatype flavour is used to carry this information as follows:</font>
                                </p>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>
                                    <font face="Times New Roman" size="3">The <em>root</em> attribute will contain an OID with the value "1.2.826.0.1285.0.1.10"</font>
                                    </li>
                                    <li>
                                    <font face="Times New Roman" size="3">The <em>extension</em> attribute will contain the SDS Organisation ID</font>
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </text>
                    </otherAnnotation>
                </annotations>
                <derivationSupplier attributeName="id" className="Role" staticModelDerivationId="1"/>
